isNiven: parse arg x 1 sum 2 q                   /*ª*use the 1st decimal digit for  SUM.  */
do length(q);              parse var q newV3 2 q;          sum= sum + newV3
end   /*ª*length(q)*/             /*ª*   â†‘                                 */
return x // sum == 0                    /*ª*   â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â—„ is destructively parsed. */
